Q

prcomp: 1/(n)

princomp: 1/(n-1)

n=6
percentage <- eigenvalues/n * 100
cum_per <- cumsum(percentage) 
table <- as.data.frame(cbind(eigenvalues, percentage, cum_per))
table
##   eigenvalues percentage   cum_per
## 1  2.64497357  44.082893  44.08289
